high_descs: turn to the right and go forward to the front of the sink and turn to the left
pick up the big spoon with the blue handle on the counter top in front of the sink
put the big spoon in the sink
turn on the water to fill up the sink and turn off the water and drain the sink and pick up the big spoon
turn to the left twice and take a few steps and turn to the right twice
open the right cabinet door underneath the sink and put the big spoon in it and close the cabinet door
anns.task_desc: Place a washed big spoon with a blue handle in a cabinet underneath a sink

high_descs: Turn right and walk a few feet over to the kitchen sink
Pick up the golden spoon from the edge of the counter in front of the sink
Put the spoon in the kitchen sink
Wash the spoon under water in the sink and remove it
Turn around, walk a few feet, then turn back toward the kitchen sink
Open the cabinet below the right corner of the sink and put the spoon in it
anns.task_desc: Put the washed spoon in the kitchen cabinet

high_descs: Turn to your right and move over to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the ladle that is to the right of the salt shaker.
Move closer to the sink with the ladle.
Wash the ladle off in the sink before picking it back up.
Move over to the third cabinet beneath the kitchen sink that has a drawer above it.
Open the cabinet door and place the ladle in front of the cup before shutting the door.
anns.task_desc: Move a clean ladle to a cabinet.
